  <h3>The Three Peptides at a Glance</h3>
  <p style="font-size:14px;margin-bottom:0;"><strong>BPC-157:</strong> 15 amino acids, derived from human gastric juice, targets local tissue repair &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>TB-500:</strong> 43 amino acids (Thymosin Beta-4 fragment), promotes systemic cell migration &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>GHK-Cu:</strong> Copper-binding tripeptide (Gly-His-Lys), stimulates collagen and elastin synthesis &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Combined Target:</strong> Full-spectrum tissue healing from acute injury through structural remodeling</p>
</div>

<table class="tbl">
