  This article is for educational and informational purposes only. It is not medical advice and should not be treated as such. The peptides discussed here are not FDA-approved for human therapeutic use in the United States. Always consult a qualified healthcare provider before starting any peptide protocol. Individual results vary. Do not use peptides to self-treat serious medical conditions without professional supervision.
